{"tid":1606304,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國難五金嚴正聲明","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T16:43:37.000Z","uid":296349,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32f24f9ef04766e833936c2e8400aa5da9cb316a","tid":1606304,"uid":296349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"今日(2019年9月30日) 開鋪引來大量防暴警察到場，本店內部分貨品包括《國難家書》被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n國難員工暫時不會再找各位小朋友，如有人聲稱是國難員工，各位無需理會。<br />\n<br />\n懇請各位手足曾經有交過家書，請立即改tg id ，有留電話立刻掉左張卡，以保障各位手足安全。不便之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國難五金財力雄厚，暫無需熱心人士捐款或籌款。<br />\n<br />\n如坊間有任何組織發起以國難五金為名之任何籌款活動，本公司將保留法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n本公司將無限期停止運作，直至另行通知。不便之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世上沒有從天而降的英雄，<br />\n只有挺身而出的凡人。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8bc26f05e8d20e9c7bce639ee056c2678f2d8cd4","tid":1606304,"uid":167592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52fddfe4f516742944ba0a6153dcc3ebd26dfd95","tid":1606304,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dcc53f2e7c3e607e6dd81ff16d832928a9b1f3","tid":1606304,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"心思好細密 <br />\n好聰明<br />\n<br />\n無事既"},{"pid":"7c081068f75e4e91a5a334acf5aced234ea308b0","tid":1606304,"uid":291865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rjMHWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rjMHWR.jpg&h=77247672&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ead6360596d1f46d426f15d6c5505e55c27717c","tid":160630